Exercise 1 : Spring Web Project
📄 Description:
Spring Boot web application that exposes a /greet REST endpoint using Spring Web.

📥 Sample Input (URL):
http://localhost:8080/greet

📤 Sample Output (Response):
Hello from Spring Boot!

🛠️ What is Used to Bring this Output:

Spring Boot Starter Web

SpringWebDemoApplication.java as the entry point

GreetingController.java to define /greet

Embedded Tomcat on port 8080
